dfischer.utils

Interface LogVectorInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HttpLoadTest, LogVector, ThreadSaveLogVector

    public interface LogVectorInterface
    Interface to collect ASCII/TEXT log output of a thread and to dump it later in a safe way.
    See Also:
